          },
          "reviewBody": "Aspam Scottish School, located in Sector 62 of Noida, is a well-regarded institution that is known for its commitment to providing a high-quality education to its students. The school boasts a dedicated and experienced faculty, and offers a wide range of academic programs that are designed to challenge and inspire students. The school's facilities are modern and well-maintained, providing an ideal learning environment for students. The school has a strong emphasis on extracurricular activities and sports, which helps students develop their talents and interests outside the classroom.\n\nThe school's curriculum is designed to meet the needs of the 21st century and is regularly updated to ensure that students are well-prepared for the future. The school's values of discipline, hard work, and character-building are well-inculcated in the students. The school has a strong reputation for producing well-rounded and successful graduates. The school is affiliated to CBSE board and has a diverse student body, which encourages cultural exchange and global perspective.\n\nThe school also has a counselor on board to provide emotional and psychological support to students and parents. The school's library is well-equipped with a variety of books, journals and other reference materials, providing students with a wealth of information for research and study. The school's labs are equipped with modern equipment and facilities that provide students with hands-on experience and training in various subjects.",
